{"tid":2370255,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【Steam玩家一定要擁有的遊戲】7款Steam經典代表作，你都買了嗎","createTime":"2021-01-18T01:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:47:03.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"08d1f1d076a940ddd505259ce116999b5887eea3","tid":2370255,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"Steam上這麼多遊戲，許多玩家最大的困惑就在於：我該買點啥遊戲玩？<br />\n<br />\n  不同於eShop和PS Store，Steam遊戲每天都會上架許多遊戲，你或許能叫得上名來，或許叫不上名來。但就如同《曠野之息》之於NS、《女神異聞錄5》之於PS4，每個平台都有那麼一些經典遊戲，值得所有玩家去擁有。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F1cb45621p00qmilik008yc000ht0092m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F1cb45621p00qmilik008yc000ht0092m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=67d491d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F89e24e24p00qmilik0074c000ht008xm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F89e24e24p00qmilik0074c000ht008xm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=60246e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  1.《GTA V》&mdash;&mdash;是誰還沒買《GTA 5》？<br />\n<br />\n  讓我康康是誰還沒有買《GTA 5》？即使Epic免費送了，Steam一打折，《GTA 5》依然能殺回到銷量榜中。就看看這銷量，1.35億，全世界才多少打遊戲的？排在《GTA 5》前面的，只有《我的世界》和《俄羅斯方塊》這兩個怪物&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2Fabadf1d8j00qmilik001ic000ht00dbm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252Fabadf1d8j00qmilik001ic000ht00dbm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8895477f&s={SIZE}\" />[/img]<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  再配合上PC端得天獨厚的神優化+MOD，讓遊戲持續多年依然具有活力。R星更是乾脆把這款首發在PS3平台上的遊戲要帶到PS5平台&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  遙想當年，PS2上出了3款《GTA》，然後《GTA 5》一款遊戲就登了3個平台&hellip;&hellip;比較可惜的是PC端《GTA OL》的遊戲環境比較差&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F95199596j00qmilik000rc000hs00a0m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F95199596j00qmilik000rc000hs00a0m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=7e4666f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  不說了，Steam庫裡還沒有《GTA 5》的舉個手，拖出去打死&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  2.《巫師3》&mdash;&mdash;求求蠢驢賺點錢吧<br />\n<br />\n  CDPR可以說想方設法想讓玩家買《巫師3》。除了遊戲素質極高外，無敵的性價比也造就了《巫師3》的成功。Steam常年打折年度版40多元、有其他版免費送GOG版、免費跨時代還新增光追&hellip;&hellip;這麼良心還不買一份？<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2Fff73c684p00qmilik008bc000ht008vm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252Fff73c684p00qmilik008bc000ht008vm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=97d54093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  要是想補全系列，還可以花5塊買《巫師1》和《巫師2》；哦對，《巫師1》也動不動就免費送&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F43d96af0p00qmilik009wc000ht0091m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F43d96af0p00qmilik009wc000ht0091m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=bdf267a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  《巫師3》的開放世界設計可能不是最出色的，但絕對是最具歐洲中世紀魔幻色彩的。每次騎著馬漫步在陶森特，我總是會感慨：能玩到《巫師3》真是玩家的福氣啊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  類似遊戲：《上古捲軸5》《刺客信條：奧德賽》<br />\n<br />\n  3.《魔鏡Mirror》&mdash;&mdash;最良心，業界模範<br />\n<br />\n  Steam上最靚麗的風景線無疑就是&mdash;&mdash;種類繁多的小黃油。但你問我哪款最最最值得買，我首推《魔鏡》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F741a7c4fp00qmilik007mc000ht008xm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F741a7c4fp00qmilik007mc000ht008xm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8c223ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  相比於其他簡單粗暴想讓你衝，到最后索然無味，《魔鏡》可不同。《魔鏡》不僅妹子們的立繪都很出色漂亮，而且還提供了不錯的劇情故事、雙結局、緊張刺激的連連看遊戲&hellip;&hellip;想推倒主角們也沒有那麼容易呢。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F3d9662f5p00qmilik0071c000ht008rm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F3d9662f5p00qmilik0071c000ht008rm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=f55accf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  更別說常年打折只要4元的價格，這價格能買到這個素質的遊戲，還要啥自行車？。在疫情最嚴重的時候《魔鏡》官方乾脆直接送了十幾萬份給國內玩家，讓大家安心在家玩遊戲不要外出。就衝這操作，庫存裡沒有一份怎麼行？<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  類似遊戲：《貓娘樂園》《LOVE&sup3; -愛立方-》<br />\n<br />\n  4.《三色繪戀》&mdash;&mdash;性價比最高Galgame<br />\n<br />\n  作為Galgame愛好者，雖然見識過《Clannad》的動人，領略過《Island》的驚艷，感受過《命運石之門》的高燃，但最容易安利出去的，還是《三色繪戀》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2Fc9f64213j00qmilij001nc000ht00bvm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252Fc9f64213j00qmilij001nc000ht00bvm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=586abe05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  國產的Galgame這麼些年來不斷進步，著實讓我欣喜不已。《三色繪戀》的良心更是值得Steam玩家擁有的理由&mdash;&mdash;常年打折4元、配音、作畫都非常到位，人設塑造更是不遜於日廠，現在網上依然有文芷黨和小菊黨的爭論&mdash;&mdash;是不是有《白色相簿》內味了？<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F6e46eb8fj00qmilik0017c000dw0099m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F6e46eb8fj00qmilik0017c000dw0099m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=c8e69ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  《三色繪戀》是我個人Galgame遊戲史上濃重的一筆，我真心建議所有人都去買了玩一玩，除非你是打死也不玩Galgame的人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  類似遊戲：《高考戀愛100天》《千戀＊萬花》《蒼之彼方的四重奏》"},{"pid":"4d6dc80d1962bda30a194d97e3d914d3a9a5a968","tid":2370255,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:27:01.000Z","msg":"5.《山》&mdash;&mdash;Steam四大名著之首<br />\n<br />\n  我不知道我為什麼要買這款遊戲，但是我還是買了。直到現在，我依然未能參透《山》的含義&mdash;&mdash;這簡單壁紙模擬器的背後到底有著怎樣的哲學？不過似乎有點能理解明朝聖人王陽明對著竹子&ldquo;格物致知&rdquo;的心情了。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F00c88b22p00qmilik004lc000ht008xm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F00c88b22p00qmilik004lc000ht008xm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=13dd4158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  作為Steam四大名著之首，我似乎也說不出什麼一定要買《山》的理由，但是我就是買了。要說遊戲性，其實也不是沒有，通過不同的按鍵秘籍你也能讓《山》變成音遊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  有大佬說《山》不是一款商品，而是一種心境。當然我境界太低，不能對著這遊戲發幾千小時呆然後洋洋灑灑寫心得，但是我可以推薦給大家&mdash;&mdash;8元即可入手！如果你們誰懂《山》，請務必留下你的觀點&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n  6.《Wallpaper Engine》&mdash;&mdash;不解釋<br />\n<br />\n  懂得都懂，不懂的說了也不懂，你也別問，利益牽扯太大，說了對你們沒好處，我只能說水很深，網上的資料都刪了，所以我只能說懂得都懂，不懂也沒辦法。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2Fcadadf13p00qmilik006jc000ht008wm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252Fcadadf13p00qmilik006jc000ht008wm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=6ab94c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  言歸正傳，嚴格來說這屬於軟件而不是遊戲。相比於市面上亂七八糟的壁紙軟件，我覺得，如果你但凡有那麼一點愛美之心，入手《Wallpaper Engine》時都不會有絲毫猶豫；甚至單純瀏覽壁紙，都是一種視覺享受。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F503334d0p00qmilik006uc000ht008um.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F503334d0p00qmilik006uc000ht008um.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=e3ba944f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  7.《求生之路2》&mdash;&mdash;重獲新生的經典<br />\n<br />\n  作為V社的看家法寶之一，雖然由於G胖不愛數三的壞毛病讓《求生之路2》顯得有些&ldquo;老&rdquo;了，但本作在十幾年間始終保持活力，甚至還將推出一次大型更新。而更新正是推出的社區地圖。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F82652afbj00qmilij000pc000ht00b4m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F82652afbj00qmilij000pc000ht00b4m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=aef7c549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  作為當年網吧最火爆的遊戲之一，筆者年少時期的一大樂趣就是和朋友在放學後開黑搓一會《求生之路2》。4人合作大戰殭屍，在當時是如此新穎的設計，而遊戲玩法設計直到現在也不過時，即使被眾多廠商模仿，但最能喚起玩家共鳴的，依然是《求生之路2》。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0106%2F00fae80aj00qmilik001ic000ht00b5m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0106%252F00fae80aj00qmilik001ic000ht00b5m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=1c505266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  和《COD》不同，相信許多人購買《求生之路2》並不是單純為了補票，而是真的希望能以現在的心態和眼光重新審視這款經典遊戲。社區內層出不窮的MOD也讓老粉絲愛不釋手。<br />\n<br />\n  相比於《傳送門》《半條命》，我更推崇《求生之路2》。<br />\n<br />\n  類似遊戲：《彩虹六號：圍攻》《CS：GO》<br />\n<br />\n  以上就是本期的「Steam玩家必買遊戲」了~由此可見Steam平台的強大&mdash;&mdash;玩大作、偷偷玩小黃油、學習、甚至鑽研哲學&hellip;&hellip;而以上則是個人認為最具代表性的幾款遊戲&mdash;&mdash;可以不玩，但是不能沒有。"},{"pid":"f0fb758b262c880baaeaf23d3d2154dcb484c129","tid":2370255,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:30:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人玩過saint row 2 我覺得正過GTA5 雖然係單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b807aa473daaa036f6436c0080d027c50c4679c2","tid":2370255,"uid":10901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"三色繪戀????????????"},{"pid":"f88f2c8fc20385e47a27f3c5de283e2456fc47d5","tid":2370255,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"Pubg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39a1d64f6cb7c0be643be02f99eee26cb0ddafb","tid":2370255,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"7199a91596a38ff1bb2d08a0080aa56f8ba1501f","tid":2370255,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:39:31.000Z","msg":"得6同7有<br />\n你可以拖我出去打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"